{"tid":1808274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警謊江Sir :扯開許智峰眼罩再噴胡椒噴霧先有驅散作用！！","createTime":"2020-01-02T09:16:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T09:31:57.000Z","uid":22556,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"412c0074090dc7880c7090ff53494f4b98b0fa1e","tid":1808274,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:16:23.000Z","msg":"民主黨立法會議員許智峯昨晚（1月1日）在元旦大遊行結束後，於銅鑼灣軒尼詩道及渣甸街交界行人路與警員理論，被防暴警員兩度扯開眼罩，及遭多次近距離噴射胡椒噴劑。警察公共關係科高級警司（媒體聯絡及傳訊）江永祥今日在警方記者會上解釋，當時許不合作，「消極抵抗」，又指許有帶眼罩，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「唔知係咪佢恃住自己有帶眼罩，所以唔係好怕我哋胡椒噴劑，所以同事拉開眼罩，使用胡椒噴劑。令到驅散行動更有效。」</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n江永祥指出，昨晚上 7 時許，銅鑼灣怡和街警及波斯富街附近掃蕩，大部分人堵路、叫囂、挑釁警務人員，警員多次用藍旗黑旗警告，人群拒絕聽從指示；至 8 時許，為恢復道路秩序，警方進行驅散要求和平離去，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「你所講嗰名男子</span></span></strong>（許智峯），喺過程中拒絕離開，唔離開不特止，仲要唔聽從我哋指示。」<br />\n<br />\n江永祥又指，過程中曾要求許回到行人路，「唔合作，消極抵抗，繼續糾纏，同事曾經畀過警告，同佢講如果再唔離開，我哋可能會使用胡椒噴劑進行驅散。當時呢個人有戴眼罩，唔知係咪佢恃住自己有帶眼罩，所以唔係好怕我哋胡椒噴劑，所以同事拉開眼罩，使用胡椒噴劑。令到驅散行動更有效。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E6%89%AF%E8%B5%B0%E8%A8%B1%E6%99%BA%E5%B3%AF%E7%9C%BC%E7%BD%A9%E5%99%B4%E6%A4%92-%E6%B1%9F%E6%B0%B8%E7%A5%A5-%E6%8B%89%E9%96%8B%E7%9C%BC%E7%BD%A9-%E9%A9%85%E6%95%A3%E6%9B%B4%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2589%25AF%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%25B3%25AF%25E7%259C%25BC%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E5%2599%25B4%25E6%25A4%2592-%25E6%25B1%259F%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E7%25A5%25A5-%25E6%258B%2589%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%259C%25BC%25E7%25BD%25A9-%25E9%25A9%2585%25E6%2595%25A3%25E6%259B%25B4%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2595%2588%2F&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPmipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=e5d0ebbd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2589%25AF%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%25B3%25AF%25E7%259C%25BC%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E5%2599%25B4%25E6%25A4%2592-%25E6%25B1%259F%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E7%25A5%25A5-%25E6%258B%2589%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%259C%25BC%25E7%25BD%25A9-%25E9%25A9%2585%25E6%2595%25A3%25E6%259B%25B4%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2595%2588%2F&h=430e1f92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E6%89%AF%E8%B5%B0%E8%A8%B1%E6%99%BA%E5%B3%AF%E7%9C%BC%E7%BD%A9%E5%99%B4%E6%A4%92-%E6%B1%9F%E6%B0%B8%E7%A5%A5-%E6%8B%89%E9%96%8B%E7%9C%BC%E7%BD%A9-%E9%A9%85%E6%95%A3%E6%9B%B4%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88/</a>"},{"pid":"73604aad6b854f98bde2c0bbb4083ba34a7ac85b","tid":1808274,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:18:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e16c1f93287a06d16e9247d6f7695a980226cd2","tid":1808274,"uid":34189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:20:03.000Z","msg":"你班仆街恃住自己有槍唔聽民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0024a348908c920a599ae71345c6e2aedd6024","tid":1808274,"uid":48942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:20:11.000Z","msg":"根據佢啲歪理，遲啲開槍唔係射軀幹，槍槍爆頭，令到驅散行動更有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8e434a499f7ff72dd521a089184697f275e459","tid":1808274,"uid":56567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:20:13.000Z","msg":"顏色水係咪要除嘥衫先射？<br />\n催淚彈係咪要整開嗰口，對眼先射？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c29224cc77a6a5585a95b9717e721be3fa3c108","tid":1808274,"uid":96648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:26:16.000Z","msg":"sir 你老母"},{"pid":"e91836c09906eda16c89f360f65de8c1e0acd4f3","tid":1808274,"uid":276393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:28:25.000Z","msg":"你老母肛門蛇食💩"},{"pid"